43}, {\"ngram\": \"Rankin and Long's granddaughter\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3276}, {\"ngram\": \"dinner\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3291}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"very special meal\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3340}, {\"ngram\": \"a very special conversation\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We both spoke to what it was like to be the grandchild of an Olympian, particularly an Olympian from those Games and particularly our respective grandfathers and only Julia could speak to what it's like in a way that's similar to how I could speak to what it's like,\\\" remembers Rankin.\", \"from\": 3373, \"to\": 3659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3435, \"end\": 3443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999998826752, \"rank\": 1.1718249516357662e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3461, \"end\": 3469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999998826752, \"rank\": 1.1718249516357662e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3541, \"end\": 3546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"score\": 0.9999999999522515, \"rank\": 4.735874917514086e-11, \"text\": \"Julia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\"}, {\"begin\": 3652, \"end\": 3658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Rankin\", \"score\": 0.9999139468102464, \"rank\": 8.606059566452203e-05, \"text\": \"Rankin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Rankin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Rankin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the grandchild\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3428}, {\"ngram\": \"those Games\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3486}, {\"ngram\": \"particularly our respective grandfathers\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3531}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And so, we of course bonded over that.\", \"from\": 3661, \"to\": 3700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We talked about our personal interests that are likely to have been influenced by our grandfathers, our interests in outdoors and physicality and sports.\", \"from\": 3701, \"to\": 3854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our personal interests\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3739}, {\"ngram\": \"our grandfathers\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3799}, {\"ngram\": \"our interests\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 3814}, {\"ngram\": \"physicality\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3842}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 3847, \"to\": 3853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it was, it was a very special time and a very special conversation and the connection continues on today.\\\"\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very special time\", \"from\": 3873, \"to\": 3892}, {\"ngram\": \"the connection\", \"from\": 3929, \"to\": 3943}, {\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 3962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the Berlin Games, widespread, institutionalized racism and segregation in the US meant Owens' achievements were not fully appreciated when he returned home.\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 4128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4050, \"end\": 4052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998532863615691, \"rank\": 0.0001372304218337076, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Berlin Games\", \"from\": 3972, \"to\": 3988}, {\"ngram\": \"widespread, institutionalized racism\", \"from\": 3990, \"to\": 4026}, {\"ngram\": \"segregation\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4042}, {\"ngram\": \"Owens' achievements\", \"from\": 4059, \"to\": 4078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although the then-22-year-old Owens did receive a New York ticker tape parade, he was forced to ride in a freight elevator to a reception in his honor at the Waldorf Astoria hotel.\", \"from\": 4130, \"to\": 4310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4180, \"end\": 4188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999993262065342, \"rank\": 6.737927282061741e-07, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 4288, \"end\": 4303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waldorf_Astoria_New_York\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.790122039894237e-38, \"text\": \"Waldorf Astoria\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q27686\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waldorf_Astoria_New_York\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waldorf_Astoria_New_York\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the then-22-year-old Owens\", \"from\": 4139, \"to\": 4165}, {\"ngram\": \"a freight elevator\", \"from\": 4234, \"to\": 4252}, {\"ngram\": \"a reception\", \"from\": 4256, \"to\": 4267}, {\"ngram\": \"his honor\", \"from\": 4271, \"to\": 4280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Although I wasn't invited to shake hands with Hitler,\\\" Owens said, \\\"I wasn't invited to the White House to shake hands with the President, either.\\\"\", \"from\": 4312, \"to\": 4460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4359, \"end\": 4365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.437848785093362e-14, \"text\": \"Hitler\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\", \"dbpedia\": \"h